Maintainer: Marcus Young <M.A.Young@soton.ac.uk>
Description: Open Trip Planner for R is an interface for the Open Trip Planner <http://www.opentripplanner.org/>
    OpenTripPlanner (OTP) is an open source platform for multi-modal and multi-agency journey planning written in Java.
    OTP provides a REST API which Open Trip Planner for R uses to connect to OTP.
